column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid, p.ra, p.dec, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field, s.specobjid, s.class, s.z AS redshift, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid FROM PhotoObjAll AS p JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE  (s.class = &&& OR s.class = &&&) AND s.z BETWEEN # AND # AND s.snmedian_g > #
